    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein B6 dampers with refreshed bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains thermally stable and delivers linear torque throughout the rev range. A robust, mechanically sound platform for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
